Class Ed25519Field

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.proximax.core.crypto.ed25519.arithmetic.Ed25519Field

  • public class Ed25519Field
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents the underlying finite field for Ed25519. The field has p = 2^255 - 19 elements.
